sentences.sContent: Massive tractors and bulldozers are ripping into the treeline, toppling the huge trees.
sentences.sContent_eng: Massive tractors and bulldozers are ripping into the treeline, toppling the huge trees.
sentences.sCn: 巨型拖拉机和推土机正在切割树木线，巨大的树木被放倒。

sentences.sContent: Vegetation lines the slopes at lower elevations, but much of the land in this image lies above the treeline.
sentences.sContent_eng: Vegetation lines the slopes at lower elevations, but much of the land in this image lies above the treeline.
sentences.sCn: 植被沿着山坡较低处生长，然而图中的大部分陆地位于林线以上。

trans.tranCn: 林木线（山顶上树木生长的上限）
